commit.message: Fix #174: Improve popitem() exception context handling.
Fix #164: Support cache_parameters() with cachetools.func decorators.
Fix #163: Support user_function with cachetools.func decorators.
Fix #135: Document how to use shared caches with @cachedmethod.
Fix #130: Fix pickling/unpickling of cache keys.
Fix #123: Use time.monotonic as default timer if available.
Fix #118: Improve documentation regarding thread safety.
Fix #113: Add support for maxsize=None in cachetools.func decorators.
Fix #54: Add note regarding thread safety.
